lease Ready] | [All tests pass] | [Date/Phase] |\n274: <!-- /ANCHOR:milestones -->\n275: \n276: ---\n277: \n278: ## L3: ARCHITECTURE DECISION RECORD\n279: \n280: ### ADR-001: [Decision Title]\n281: \n282: **Status**: [Proposed/Accepted/Deprecated]\n283: \n284: **Context**: [What problem we're solving]\n285: \n286: **Decision**: [What we decided]\n287: \n288: **Consequences**:\n289: - [Positive outcome 1]\n290: - [Negative outcome + mitigation]\n291: \n292: **Alternatives Rejected**:\n293: - [Option B]: [Why rejected]\n294: \n295: ---\n296: \n297: <!--\n298: LEVEL 3 PLAN (~200 lines)\n299: - Core + L2 + L3 addendums\n300: - Dependency graphs, milestones\n301: - Architecture decision records\n302: -->\n303: \n304: \n305: <!-- SCAFFOLD_AI_PROTOCOL_MARKERS:\n306: AI EXECUTION\n307: Pre-Task Checklist\n308: Execution Rules\n309: Status Reporting Format\n310: Blocked Task Protocol\n311: -->\n\n(End of file - total 311 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\ntitle: \"Implementation Plan: Deep research round 2 to map every public-repo surface and optimization that moves our AIs toward fable-5 efficiency, from the fable-mode and opus-fable-mode sources [template:level_3/plan.md]\"\ndescription: \"[2-3 sentences: what this implements and the technical approach]\"\ntrigger_phrases:\n  - \"implementation\"\n  - \"plan\"\n  - \"name\"\n  - \"template\"\n  - \"plan core\"\nimportance_tier: \"normal\"\ncontextType: \"general\"\n_memory:\n  continuity:\n    packet_pointer: \"scaffold/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research\"\n    last_updated_at: \"2026-06-15T09:00:05Z\"\n    last_updated_by: \"template-author\"\n    recent_action: \"Initialized Level 3 template\"\n    next_safe_action: \"Replace continuity placeholders\"\n    blockers: []\n    key_files: []","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency